 "description": "Huge and hungry, lurking just beneath the land's surface nearly everywhere — up to 50 feet long and near 10 feet around. The tail bears a poisonous sting, but the mouth is worse: it gulps down ogre-sized prey whole. Any hit exceeding by 20% the minimum needed — or any 100% hit — means the victim is swallowed: dead in six turns, digested beyond recovery in twelve. Purple Worms never check morale and always attack.",
